Clear data from a specific range in a Google Sheet. I'll need:
1. Spreadsheet ID or name (if name, search for it first)
2. Range to clear (in A1 notation like "A1:C10" or "Sheet1!A1:C10")

Use the clear_range tool to remove all data from the specified range.

